    "(5) Applying the DCT with zigzag scanning to acquire spectral demonstration and reduce fused features obtained from the different CNNs.",
    "(6) Evaluating the classification performance for different feature lengths using analysis of variance (ANOVA) feature selection to select the optimum feature length that provides the best accuracy.",
    "(7) Color-CADx executes the classification process autonomously, eliminating the need to specify disease regions or execute any segmentation procedure.",
    "The subsequent sections of the paper are organized as follows.",
    "Section \"Related works\" presents relevant research studies that developed CAD models for the diagnosis of CRC."
